Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{part a}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:37.26,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,考えるな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.21,0:00:40.49,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,深く考えるな 霧島海人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't think too hard about it, Kirishima Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That wasn't a confession yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.51,0:00:44.45,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日は別に 先輩に告白したわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She didn't even realize what I meant the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:48.70,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一昨日のことだって 先輩は気づいてなかったじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:51.41,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,平常心よ イチカ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm older than him. I have to keep my cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:55.43,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君より 年上の私がしっかりしなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.44,0:00:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just make him breakfast like always
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:58.71,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いつものように 朝食を作って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and put a bit of effort into cooking up lunchboxes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:00.13,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょっと 頑張って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.23,0:01:02.17,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お弁当なんかも作ってみたり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.53,0:01:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, nothing is weird about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.56,0:01:04.78,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうさ なんの問題もない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:08.08,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この家に 先輩が同居しているってだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're just sharing the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:09.47,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:11.66,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,自然体よ イチカ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be yourself, Ichika. Like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:13.50,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あくまで自然体に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:15.42,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いつも通りに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:20.81,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,平常心 平常心 平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Be cool. Be cool. Be cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:24.66,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は やれば出来る子だから 自信持って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do so much. Working up some courage can't be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe I shouldn't put myself in such a great light...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.08,0:01:27.44,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや 出来る子って変かな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.57,0:01:27.94,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,むしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:28.89,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おはようございます
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:32.79,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お おはよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... such a lovely day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.96,0:01:34.88,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,い いい天気ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.12,0:01:36.52,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうですね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's hardly a cloud in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:37.97,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今日は 晴れますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.13,0:01:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:39.44,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうですね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:43.48,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もうすぐ 期末テストです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Finals are coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:45.51,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうですね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.09,0:01:48.30,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,勉強は苦手です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm bad at studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:49.87,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうですか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even remember what I had for breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:58.63,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,朝 何食ったかも覚えてねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.69,0:02:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Kirishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:00.72,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おはよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.17,0:02:02.34,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,霧島君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally you wake up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:04.79,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,珍しく 早起きなんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.46,0:02:06.56,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,た たまにはね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:10.59,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ 谷川 昨日はごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tanigawa. Sorry about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.09,0:02:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We never met up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:13.13,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,逸れたまま それきりになって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't apologize. It was my fault too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:16.47,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ううん 私のほうこそごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:19.97,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,っていうか 檸檬先輩や美桜が悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it was all Lemon and Mio's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologized yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:23.13,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日も散々謝った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, get this, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:25.67,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだ 聞いてよ 海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.05,0:02:28.70,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日 檸檬先輩だけじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemon is one thing, but Tetsuro and Mio were stalking me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:32.24,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎や美桜も私のこと覗いてたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:33.98,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ そうなの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kirishima...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:36.23,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい 霧島君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:37.48,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや 別に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:40.21,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何かあったの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Something? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:42.42,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,な 何かって何が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.81,0:02:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not your usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:45.29,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いつもと態度が違うから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:47.57,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そ そ そうかな そんなことないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:49.06,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いたって普通だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being perfectly normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you were in Karuizawa yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:56.85,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日 軽井沢に行ったんですって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:02:59.17,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ まあ うん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:03:02.49,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(566,176)\blur0.7\fs50\1a&H20&\fscy125\fax0.15\fnsqueaky chalk sound\frz344.741\c&HA9A397&\frx0\fry346}Study  {\fax0.1}Time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:00.62,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何しに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a bit of shopping to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:02.38,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,買い物をちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirishima was there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:04.39,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,霧島君もいたわ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:07.57,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,軽井沢に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In Karuizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:09.95,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そ そう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:14.28,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,霧島君 霧島君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:20.69,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,面白いわ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet she's uncomfortable now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:32.70,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やっぱ 困らしちゃってんだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:35.48,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ううん そんなことない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It just caught me off guard.{ends at douyou shiteta}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:40.87,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,突然だったから 動揺しただけなの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually like you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:44.15,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私だって 海人君のことが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:46.00,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,マジっすか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:48.54,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,マジっすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! It's mutual!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:52.30,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,わい 両思いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:54.46,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't swing that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:56.82,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺にそっちの趣味はねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how {\i1}I{\i0} should've reacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:03.91,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そりゃ俺のリアクションだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:04.80,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:06.25,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,弁当
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A lunch box?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:09.19,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さっき イチカ先輩に頼まれたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika asked me to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.57,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海に 渡してくれって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She did?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:12.99,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩が
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget it at home when she went\N through the trouble of making it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.20,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,せっかく作ってくれたもん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:16.49,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,忘れんなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:21.99,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ そうだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tetsuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.18,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あのさ 哲郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So, hypothetically speaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:30.41,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,例え話なんだけどさ
