Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:09.31,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:14.23,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちなみに A美ちゃんはB太君のことをどう思っているの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So how does Ms. A feel about Mr. B?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.49,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,決して嫌っているわけではありません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't dislike him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She thinks he's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:20.40,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,可愛いとさえ思っているようです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why not go out with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:22.70,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なら オーケーすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:26.37,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,問題はそう簡単ではありません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:27.49,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:29.25,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Ms. A will...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:31.21,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,A美ちゃんが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:39.98,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いずれ この町を離れてしまうからです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually have to leave the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. B is definitely uncomfortable,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:49.97,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,B子ちゃんは確かに困ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have no idea whether she wishes it'd all go away, or she just doesn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:53.35,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,けど 迷惑に感じてるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:56.53,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ただ単に困惑してるだけなのか 分かんねえし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:06:00.34,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,A男君は 結果を焦らないほうがいいと思うぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:06:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'd be best if Mr. A didn't rush things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.86,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,焦るな か
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not rush things, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.85,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,サボり魔 発見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I spy a little slacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:07.50,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あ 谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tanigawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? You tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:09.57,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何 疲れちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:10.95,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょっとな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you never finished telling me what happened to you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:17.79,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あのさ 今朝 聞きそびれちゃったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:20.59,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日 逸れたあと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So what did you do afterward?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:23.18,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何してた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I got bored and went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:26.05,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ しかたなく 家に戻ったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:27.14,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:28.17,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:30.49,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,探してくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you go looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:35.48,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あら 霧島君と谷川さんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Kirishima and Tanigawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:40.26,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんだ 檸檬先輩か
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just you, Lemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite the greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:41.84,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ご挨拶ね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:44.83,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,魅力的な年上の女性が
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have nothing else to say about an attractive upperclassmen and her alluring swimsuit-clad body?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:48.19,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,妖艶な水着姿を晒しているというのに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Alluring?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:49.77,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,妖艶って
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a normal school swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:51.83,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ただのスク水ですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.56,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,檸檬 集合だって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we're supposed to assemble...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.20,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,い 行きましょう 檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:07:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Lemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:07.64,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,A美ちゃんには C子ちゃんってライバルがいるみたいね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem that Ms. A has a rival called Ms. C.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.47,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ なんのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are things still pretty awkward between you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:18.67,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もしかして まだ貴月先輩とギクシャクしてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:20.89,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ まあ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:23.39,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君 しっかりしなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She's isn't from this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:27.64,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そりゃ 貴月先輩は外国の人だから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so she might be having trouble communicating or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.50,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,コミニケーションとか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:31.94,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いろいろと問題があるかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:36.15,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でもね 先輩は一人でこの国に来て
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And since she came here all alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,she just might be feeling scared or lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:40.12,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,不安だったり 寂しい思いをしてるんじゃないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be there to support her as best you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:43.97,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そこは 海人君がフォローしてあげないと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:47.23,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:50.12,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん 谷川の言う通りだと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only been thinking about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.42,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺 自分のことばっか考えてた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:55.83,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それじゃ だめだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was pretty selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:08:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's good that you think about others' feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:08:01.10,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,けど 相手の人のことをちゃんと考える海人君はいいと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:02.62,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:04.05,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,頑張れ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, Ms. C over there just shot herself in the foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:10.61,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,わあ C子ちゃん 地雷踏みっぱなしだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. C?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:12.27,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,C子ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:24.21,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しっかりしなきゃ しっかり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to get my act together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:31.04,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,イチカ先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.07,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,な 何かしら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.76,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日のことなんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,About what happened yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I acted the way I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.99,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺 変な態度取っちゃって すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:40.49,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも そういう意味じゃないですから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not what I meant back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:41.78,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,気にしないでください
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:43.92,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:46.75,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから 普段通りで行きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's pretend it never happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.12,0:08:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It never happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.95,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,普段通りにする
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:51.42,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よし これだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, things'll be back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:54.16,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,このパタンで現状を打破する
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:57.55,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺はやれる やるんだ やらなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:58.67,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:08:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}want {\i0}to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you that horny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.47,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなに堪ってんの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.03,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ええ そりゃもう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:06.06,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,で えっ 真 真奈美さん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma-Manami?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help you with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:09.29,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんなら あたしが相手してあげようか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:10.74,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんのです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:15.97,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,意味分かんない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't feign innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:18.05,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,純情ぶっちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:19.23,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まあいいか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai, I'm going shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:22.19,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海 あたし買い物の途中なの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Cum}Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:23.52,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,付き合ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a choice, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:27.29,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,反論なし でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.70,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ご明察
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito, I was really happy to hear how you felt about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:31.86,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:35.65,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君の気持ちはとっても嬉しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But we just met,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:40.03,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 私たちは まだ 出会ったばっかりで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so could you give me some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:44.00,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから お返事は少し時間をもらえないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give it some thought before giving you my answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:48.05,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君のことをよく考えて ちゃんと返事します
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's act like normal until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:51.35,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それまでは いつも通りでいましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:56.12,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい 分かりました 先輩の言うことに従います
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:59.59,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん こんな感じで話せば
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:05.67,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:08.10,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの女性は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.76,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ど どういうこと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But yesterday he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:15.34,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日は私に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:19.20,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そりゃ ちゃんと返事をしなかった私もいけないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's my fault for not giving him my answer yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it hasn't even been a day, and he's already on a date with another woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:24.36,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日の今日で もう違う女の人とデートしてるのなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:26.37,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,信じられない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I was stupid for even worrying about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:30.40,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,悩んでいた私がバカみたいじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:32.38,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もう 勝手にすればいいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:42.92,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,りのん リンゲージで私をシャンプさせて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me jump with the quantum link.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you bail on me again, you're going into the stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:50.07,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今日こそ応答してくれないと どうなるか分からないわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:58.47,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,りのん これは あれなの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:11:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinon, we're doing this only because Sistersis asked me to take care of Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:02.05,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃんさんに 海人君のことを頼まれたから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:03.81,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よろしくねって言われたから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She left him in my care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. That's all there is to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:07.55,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それだけ それだけなんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:14.92,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(873,427)\fs70\blur0.55}You Were Amazing{\b1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:14.92,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(545,369)\blur0.55}Episode Four
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This and this. And this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:18.96,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これとこれ ああ これも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're buying a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:20.30,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなに買うの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a real fight this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:22.53,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今回は長期戦だから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:25.78,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうですか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:31.21,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,で 次はどこ行くんです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where to next?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:32.89,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょ 真奈美さん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:34.26,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,嬉しいくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:38.68,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あ あんなに大胆に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They're walking around like {\i1}that{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:49.21,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:55.67,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの まだですか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai, wanna check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:58.52,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海 見たい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:11:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:11:59.68,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:01.09,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どう 似合う
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a perfect fit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.42,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ええ もう ばっちりですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just buy it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:05.79,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから と とと とっとと買っちゃってください
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:36.95,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:39.42,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:45.73,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人 こっちにいらっしゃい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:46.71,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:48.85,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いい子ね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:57.36,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どう イチカって子より 私のほうが全然いいでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm way better than that Ichika girl, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.07,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もちろんです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't even bother giving you an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:05.26,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,告っても 返事もしてくれない女のことなんか 忘れちゃいなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Just forget about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:06.85,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:12.13,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,りのん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a quick shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:17.11,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あたし シャワー浴びるから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:19.14,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,勝手にお茶でも飲んでて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Make yourself some tea or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:24.17,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海 一緒に入る
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna take one with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:27.49,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,心より遠慮します
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I must decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:29.17,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,可愛くないわね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not cute at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to talk to her when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:35.23,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,帰ったら 先輩に言わないとな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:35.87,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何を
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.29,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,せ 先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:43.00,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:45.45,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなことはどうでもいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:46.58,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:47.85,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,帰るわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:48.55,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I said we're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:49.84,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいから 帰るの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:52.51,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょっ ちょっと 待ってくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:54.87,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなにここにいたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to stay here that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:57.99,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,で でも 挨拶ぐらいは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I should at least say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:13:59.89,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:01.98,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,バカ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:08.04,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:12.14,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで 私 こんなに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:16.35,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あのう 先輩 なんか 誤解して
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Hey, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:17.66,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何バタバタしてんの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:19.93,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,誰 この子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who's she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.89,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もしかして 海の
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe your girlfr—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:22.70,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,違う（違います）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:23.94,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ 何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sistersis asked me to take care of Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:28.96,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,わ 私は お姉ちゃんさんから 海人君のことを頼まれているものです
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.23,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,七海から
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami did?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:32.86,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうです ですから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I can't allow him to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:35.33,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここに 海人君をいさせるわけにはいきません
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:36.62,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩 あの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito, you shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:37.69,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君は黙ってて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:38.24,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:41.76,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん いいじゃない 恋愛は自由よ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the fuss? Love is free.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem a lot older.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:44.21,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,随分と年上のようですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:46.44,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,歳の差なんて 関係ないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Age doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito is in high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.45,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君は高校生です
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Love overcomes all obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:50.83,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,愛に障害はつきものよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami, what are you talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:52.52,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈美さん 何を言って
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kaito, you shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:53.91,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君は黙ってて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.07,0:14:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:54.71,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:56.13,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:57.25,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何がですか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:58.83,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お邪魔なの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting in his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:02.82,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は海人君を守る義務があるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a duty to protect Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:03.99,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:10.10,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それだけの理由で 他人の家に断りもなく 上がりこんできたわけ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you came into someone else's house without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I not supposed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.26,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,い 行けませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:13.84,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,非常識よ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:18.27,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いい加減白状したら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not just say it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:20.70,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここに来た本当の理由を
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The real reason you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:22.33,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなの ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:23.47,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本当に
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:24.54,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah really!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:28.28,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海 この子 相当鈍いわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai, this girl is pretty dim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:29.75,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.08,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前もか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just do whatever you want then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.96,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ もう勝手にすればいいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:36.54,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そういうのも 楽しい時期だろうし
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's fun at your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:40.71,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,姉ちゃん なんだよ また来たのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.65,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お 姉さん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:45.65,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ 海 イチカ先輩まで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Kai? Ichika?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought them here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:47.70,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,姉ちゃんが連れてきたの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:49.64,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まあ そんなところ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:52.13,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ まあ ゆっくりしててよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, make yourselves at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:54.52,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つうか そんな格好してんなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Put on some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.15,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,着替えろって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:57.95,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分かった 分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:16:02.61,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,石垣君 あの お姉さんって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishigaki... your sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.63,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,紹介まだなんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't introduce herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:07.35,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ 俺のお姉ちゃん 小倉真奈美です
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my sister. Ogura Manami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogura? She's got a different name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:09.73,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,小倉 苗字が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:11.11,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,結婚してますから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She's married.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But whenever they fight she comes back here to mope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:14.37,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,っていうか 姉ちゃん 旦那と喧嘩するたびに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.90,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すぐこっち戻ってきてグチグチするんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.76,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今回ばかり許さないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna forgive him this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:21.25,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,喧嘩の理由は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He erased the show I recorded!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:25.53,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの人 あたしが録画した番組 勝手に消したの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:26.33,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うわ くだんねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:27.82,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,楽しみにしてたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really looking forward to watching it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares? Go back to Satoshi's place already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.87,0:16:29.92,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいから さとしさんとこ戻れよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No apologies will do this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.54,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,土下座したって許さない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:32.26,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,許せよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've run out of patience this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:35.20,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今回という今回は ホントに愛想が尽きたわ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't!{pls no}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:35.93,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,尽きるなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose side are you on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:37.55,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あんたはどっちの見方よ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The right side!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:38.43,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,正義だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:43.33,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい ホントにごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:45.44,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あいや 大丈夫ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I made you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:49.05,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,というか 心配かけて こっちこそ すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:51.63,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,全面的に私が悪いです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:55.96,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈美さんが誤解させるようなこというから 仕方ないですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami was being misleading on purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:57.52,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さあ 行きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:04.27,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ 海人君 お詫びをさせて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me make it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:05.93,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何でもするから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything.{my dick}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:06.85,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何でも
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:08.65,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ええ 何でも
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really wanted to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:11.93,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの時 僕は
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:15.81,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本当は聞きたかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ask her then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to ask her how she feels about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:18.01,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日の返事を
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:21.75,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕のことをどう思っているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:23.15,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:26.77,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺 勉強を苦手なんです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm bad at studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:30.15,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩 教えてもらえませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you help me out?{onegai senpai}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:37.88,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん 頑張る
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do what I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You misspelled it there. That's not an "e," but an "i."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:42.34,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そこのスペル間違ってるわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:44.45,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そこは 「E」じゃなくて 「I」です
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:45.65,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Math is up after English.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:48.35,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,英語が終わったら 次は数学ね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we get some sleep, Ichika?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:53.09,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩 もう 寝ませんか 明日も学校あるし
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We have school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time until finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:55.41,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,期末テストまで 時間がないのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,With these grades, I can understand why Sistersis was worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:17:57.19,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こんな学力じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:17:59.20,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃんさんも心配するわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:01.91,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,せめて平均点以上を目指さないと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to at least get you above average.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:04.05,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,赤点じゃなきゃいいですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter as long as I don't fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the wrong attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:06.39,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そういう態度だから ダメなの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked me to help you with your studies, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:10.05,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,勉強教えてほしいって言ったの 海人君でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:11.38,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:12.88,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい 問題解いて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now solve this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shouldn't've said anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:16.97,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,言わなきゃよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:21.56,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おい 海 大丈夫か
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kai. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:22.92,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,パイが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-chik...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:24.42,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あ おっぱい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Chicks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika has a side I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:29.05,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩が ああいう性格だと思わなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:32.01,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君 勉強するわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to study!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Takatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:33.57,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,貴月先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But... it's lunch break...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:36.56,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩 今はお昼休み
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Read the book while you eat then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:39.20,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,食べながら勉強よ 時間がないの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Time is running out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:40.56,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あ はい
