Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito and Takatsuki made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:53.84,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
