Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. C isn't the sharpest tool in the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:58.50,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何するのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
