Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Summer vacation was just around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:09.29,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一生 忘れられることのない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was going to be a summer I'd never...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:13.41,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,忘れられない 夏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...ever forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:15.13,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,きっとそれは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:17.87,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,皆も同じだったと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...everyone else felt the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:20.76,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,喜びや 悲しみ 痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Happiness, sadness, and pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of that put together in one package.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:24.28,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そういうのを 全部ひっくるめて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:26.00,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,たった一度の
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A once-in-a-lifetime experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:29.32,盛夏-JP-2-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの夏が始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.77,Default,,0,0,25,,{\i1}The summer we've been waiting for...{Our summer was beginning.}
